{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_7","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/bash -lc \"sed -n '1,220p' task-plans/insight-and-guidance-task-plan.md\"","aggregated_output":"# Insight and Guidance Task Plan\n\n## Priority\n\nPriority 2\n\n## Objective\n\nMake insights actionable, persistent, and connected to real workflow changes.\n\n## Scope\n\n- usage report quality\n- topic map actions\n- word cloud usefulness\n- weekly shift guidance\n- vibe-coding advice\n\n## Tasks\n\n### Task 1 — Insight Persistence\n\n- keep reports saved locally\n- avoid loss of memory across reloads\n- expose freshness and fallback state clearly\n\n### Task 2 — Topic and Keyword Navigation\n\n- keep topic map linked to thread list\n- make keyword exploration useful for navigation, not only display\n- improve word cloud as a filter/entry point\n\n### Task 3 — Actionable Advice\n\n- turn insights into next-step guidance\n- align suggestions with actual workflow patterns\n- avoid vague or generic recommendations\n\n## Exit Criteria\n\n- insight panels survive reloads\n- users can navigate from insights to real work items\n- advice suggests concrete workflow adjustments\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
